@clubId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
@bookingId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

### List bookings — next 7 days, all clubs, all types
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/bookings
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv TOKEN}}

### List bookings — only open games (matchmaking front door)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/bookings?type=Game&open=true
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv TOKEN}}

### List bookings — only full games
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/bookings?type=Game&open=false
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv TOKEN}}

### List bookings — filtered by club
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/bookings?clubId={{clubId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv TOKEN}}

### List bookings — explicit time window
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/bookings?clubId={{clubId}}&fromUtc=2026-05-01T00:00:00Z&toUtc=2026-05-08T00:00:00Z
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv TOKEN}}

### Create booking — Game (any authenticated user)
# @name createBooking
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/clubs/{{clubId}}/bookings
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv TOKEN}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "type": "Game",
  "startsAt": "2026-05-01T18:00:00-04:00",
  "durationMinutes": 60
}

### Create booking — DayUse (ClubStaffOrAdmin enforced inside the strategy)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/clubs/{{clubId}}/bookings
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv TOKEN}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "type": "DayUse",
  "startsAt": "2026-05-01T10:00:00-03:00",
  "durationMinutes": 240,
  "courtsToOccupy": 1,
  "capacity": 16
}

### Join Booking — uses id from Create Booking
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/bookings/{{createBooking.response.body.bookingId}}/join
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv TOKEN}}

### Join Booking (manual id)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/bookings/{{bookingId}}/join
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv TOKEN}}
